  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Five suspected to have dug up treasures in the middle of the house",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Five persons who were digging for treasures in a house in Menikhinna area of \u200b\u200bKandy were arrested by a troop of the Kandy Special Task Force base, the Special Task Force said.",
        "According to information that these suspects are digging for treasures in the house, the troops have conducted this raid.",
        "The Special Task Force says that the arrested suspects are aged between 32-47 years and are residents of Kandy, Colombo and other areas.",
        "The arrested suspects have been handed over to the Menikhinna Police along with the equipment used to dig for treasure."
      ],
